plot: A delusional homeless woman is found unconscious in an acid house exhibiting a variety of symptoms which Foreman thinks she's faking.

A homeless woman collapses at an illegal rave house, Foreman blows off the consult Wilson asks for, and House is intrigued by Foreman's and Wilson's reactions. Clinic Cases: A mother with lots of kids. Since House pretends to be ill, Cuddy makes sure he ends up teaching med students about taking histories instead.—Jaxotea
